  <brief_title>Nurses Helping Sudden Cardiac Arrest Survivors Recover After Getting An Implantable Cardioverter Defibrillator (ICD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Nursing Interventions Following Sudden Cardiac Arrest</official_title>
  <sponsors>
